budget

Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • budget.Product
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SectionProduct

    public class Product
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a product. It is created from the data in the database or introduced in a form. The prices array should be sorted by date starting with the most recent before being added to the Product. It also uses classes in package dao and storage to return the product image.
    Author:
    oscar
